description:
This video show how to use Unreal Engine 5.5's animation Sequencer feature to enhance the performance and expressions in a Metahuman face animation generated by Metahuman Animator from an audio file.

An earlier video showing how to generate animation from an audio file using Metahuman Animator can be viewed at this link:
https://youtu.be/sZyfVYybVFc
